      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S CLEGANE (6) is a first starter from the Jemma Daley yard by Orson Allen out of Hara's Pandora. Expected to be well fancied and can make an immediate impact. SHORTBREAD CINDY (3) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Noble Toby (22.45) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Must be included in calculations. COME ON CRITTER (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 390m behind Jane's Magic (22.90) in a Maiden. Was in the money the start prior. Form from her last run is proving strong. Better than last start and can bounce back. DODGEM JET (4) is an Andy Graham-trained newcomer by Tommy Shelby out of Who Told Mel. Start all important from the squeeze box. Profiles well so watch market closely.",
